column44: No feedback or suggestion at this moment as I have just started learning and need more information to explore the application.
Such small portion training modules for each cockpit in a certain short duration can help each individuals to learn and implement quickly & correctly..
Nothing to add, its a good training
To provide the correct answer after the test for each questions instead of refer to the video again

Please find below my suggestion: Either the entire training courses should be divided into 3 or 4 parts Instead of 12 Or there should be a next button in place after completion of each module so that someone can land directly to the next module instead of using back buttons to reach the home page and again start the next module. May be we can save some time.
Module is good to learn something new and helpful for the organization and self growth that helps to implement in our projects.
Hope to get support when we encounter the problem.
No, thank you for the informative training on Solution NG
Overall training absolutely perfect as it's cover all every parts
No of questions can be reduced.

I'm not sure if this survey is related to the Change Request module only or to the whole SolNG training program. Some of the questions were written in an unclear way.
Its a great WBT which I was always looking for. Kudos to the team and its leader who has put in their efforts to bring out such a great tool. Looking out for more modules in future.

It is good exercise carried out. All the best
It was background noise. Did not hear the first part of each topic. It should be possible to pass to next question without having to answere correctly.
This training is very good ,expected content has been explained . still some more this kind of trainings are to be provided with some more Questions and Answers with Certification

Not exactly. Its a new tool and i believe it covers all that is required for correct and detailed reporting in project businesses that we have. Specially we have used other tool in past hence it appears to much more informative and have direct connects with SAP as well.
It is a very good tool and learning for tracking purpose.Session was managed so nicely and crisp and short.
